      <title>How this long-lost Chinese typewriter from the 1940s changed modern computing</title>
      <author>Emily Feng</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/07/05/nx-s1-5405452/chinese-typewriter-mingkwai-stanford</link>
