lt;p&gt;Air raid sirens wailed across Kyiv for eight hours into Friday morning, and many families sought shelter in underground metro stations during the Russian onslaught. At least one person was killed and more than 20 people injured across several districts of Kyiv.&lt;/p&gt;       &lt;p&gt;Officials in Kyiv said apartment blocks, schools, warehouses and railroad infrastructure &lt;a href="https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/russian-drone-attack-triggers-fire-roof-apartment-block-officials-say-2025-07-03/" target="_blank"&gt;were also damaged&lt;/a&gt; by the roughly 550 drones and 11 missiles that landed on the capital.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div id="resnx-s1-5456846-100" class="bucketwrap internallink insettwocolumn inset2col"&gt;                     &lt;!-- END CLASS="BUCKET IMG" --&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;     &lt;!-- END ID="RESNX-S1-5456846-100" CLASS="BUCKETWRAP INTERNALLINK INSETTWOCOLUMN INSET2COL " --&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Russia's defence ministry said the aerial strikes were launched in response to the "terrorist acts of the Kyiv regime." Russia has been intensifying its bombing campaign against Ukraine in recent weeks as ceasefire talks between the two nations have floundered.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-76067" class="bucketwrap image x-large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 1280;         --source-height: 702;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1280x702+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F02%2F2f%2F1498b64c4ee1aefbed5e1cd26002%2Fgettyimages-2222755059.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1280x702+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F02%2F2f%2F1498b64c4ee1aefbed5e1cd26002%2Fgettyimages-2222755059.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotc